data.description: Perfect multifamily in a prime location! This building features 8 rooms and a total of 7,500 square feet, making it a great investment opportunity with potential for improvement and renovation. With its convenient location just minutes away from downtown Miami and the international airport, this multifamily is an excellent option for those looking to invest in a property with high return potential. It's easy to show, but please note that no visits or contacts should be made without our authorization due to confidentiality reasons. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity! Contact us for more information and the complete rent roll."
